Washington's initials?

20:00.316 --> 20:03.885
There, see?
Machine-tooled.

20:03.886 --> 20:07.589
A bottle from 1775
would've been hand-engraved.

20:07.590 --> 20:10.158
- If it's that obvious,

20:10.159 --> 20:11.693
how come no one else
caught it?

20:11.694 --> 20:13.094
- Obvious?

20:13.095 --> 20:15.063
It's an impeccable forgery.

20:15.064 --> 20:17.432
- The nose knew.

20:17.433 --> 20:19.501
- Why do you
think I caught a cold?

20:19.502 --> 20:22.003
- You ungrateful
little prick!

20:22.004 --> 20:24.139
- Oh, you mean nose.

20:24.140 --> 20:25.974
- I'll pull them from
the auction.

20:25.975 --> 20:27.976
- How about the rest
of the sale?

20:27.977 --> 20:29.778
You're selling
