21:22.331 --> 21:23.331
So we have fraud...

21:23.332 --> 21:28.303
Grand theft,
counterfeiting,

21:28.304 --> 21:29.838
criminal conspiracy...

21:29.839 --> 21:31.072
- We got into it.

21:31.073 --> 21:33.375
Bing said
he'd bring everybody down.

21:33.376 --> 21:37.846
- Now, you made
that lying drunk millions,

21:37.847 --> 21:39.781
and he threatened to ruin

21:39.782 --> 21:41.850
the reputation
of your auction house.

21:41.851 --> 21:43.551
So what'd you do?

21:43.552 --> 21:45.987
Did you drop a little blue pill
in his glass?

21:45.988 --> 21:48.356
- Absolutely not!

21:48.357 --> 21:49.924
Bing was alive
when I left.

21:49.925 --> 21:52.394
He was plastered.
But he was upright.

21:52.395 --> 21:54.729
Ask his wife.

21:54.730 --> 21:56.631
Avery and
a very handsome young man

21:56.632 --> 21:59.600
