as I was leaving.

22:05.741 --> 22:09.077
Mrs. Cullman, we were
just coming up to talk to you.

22:09.078 --> 22:10.912
You didn't tell us you
brought a man home with you.

22:10.913 --> 22:14.115
- Oh, Shane Berlin.
He's one of our models.

22:14.116 --> 22:16.351
I got a little tipsy,
and he gave me a lift home.

22:16.352 --> 22:17.886
- He came inside
with you?

22:17.887 --> 22:20.055
- Yeah.
Yeah, for a couple minutes.

22:20.056 --> 22:22.557
- Do you usually
bring models home with you?

22:24.126 --> 22:26.428
- I don't sleep around,
