23:14.443 --> 23:16.778
Wow.

23:16.779 --> 23:18.446
Uh, you're here.

23:18.447 --> 23:21.415
Bing's dead.
It's time.

23:32.409 --> 23:34.509
Well,
isn't the new York finest.

23:34.510 --> 23:37.478
- We just had
to see the cellar.

23:38.947 --> 23:42.350
- Come on in.

23:42.351 --> 23:45.653
- Guess what we found.

23:45.654 --> 23:47.522
- Will you look at that?

23:47.523 --> 23:50.558
George Washington's initials
right on the bottle.

23:53.261 --> 23:55.997
- Bing Cullman was
a greedy son of a bitch.

23:55.998 --> 23:57.298
He knew enough about me
to know

23:57.299 --> 24:00.067
I'd want
George Washington's wine.

24:00.068 --> 24:02.770
Well, he rang me
a few hours before the tasting.

24:02.771 --> 24:04.472
Said if I got there
early enough,

24:04.473 --> 24:07.241
he'd put
three bottles aside.

24:07.242 --> 24:10.211
He'd give them to me
and cut out the middleman.

24:10.212 --> 24:12.747
- Ev Dilahunt.
- Mm-hmm.

24:12.748 --> 24:14.148
So I got there early,

24:14.149 --> 24:16.317
and I bought
the chateau de tour.

24:16.318 --> 24:18.186
- And?

24:18.187 --> 24:20.354
- I didn't want him dead.

24:20.355 --> 24:22.190
I wanted him in jail.

24:22.191 --> 24:24.091
I taped the whole meeting.

24:24.092 --> 24:26.460
It's all there, detective.

24:26.461 --> 24:28.763
Wine investigators,
chemists, lawyers...

24:28.764 --> 24:31.933
I had detectives
tracking him

24:31.934 --> 24:34.902
when he unearthed
kaiser's lost cellars.

24:36.905 --> 24:39.040
Bing Cullman was

24:39.041 --> 24:42.510
the Bernie madoff
of the wine world.

24:42.511 --> 24:45.913
- You had him under
surveillance in new York?

24:45.914 --> 24:47.548
- Oh, yeah.

24:47.549 --> 24:49.850
For months at a time,
he was careless.

24:49.851 --> 24:51.118
- What's this?

24:51.119 --> 24:52.920
- That turned out to
be a dead end.

24:52.921 --> 24:56.757
I thought I'd finally discovered
his counterfeit wine lab.

24:56.758 --> 25:00.094
Turns out to be his...

25:00.095 --> 25:01.395
...His f-pad.

25:01.396 --> 25:04.331
He sublet it from
a fella named Arnold binder.

25:10.839 --> 25:14.075
- Good to see
bing's the sentimental type.

25:14.076 --> 25:17.044
- I know.

25:28.957 --> 25:31.626
Condoms, lubes...

25:31.627 --> 25:34.095
No Viagra.

25:34.096 --> 25:36.998
- Oh... when it
comes to escorts,

25:36.999 --> 25:38.733
he knows what he likes.

25:38.734 --> 25:41.702
- Farmer's daughter
escort service.

25:45.540 --> 25:46.641
- Last e-mail...

25:46.642 --> 25:49.644
"Send Emily."

25:49.645 --> 25:52.213
- It is nor hand,
nor foot, nor arm,

25:52.214 --> 25:54.582
nor any other
part belonging to man...

25:54.583 --> 25:57.018
Oh, be some other name!

25:57.019 --> 25:58.686
What's in a name?

25:58.687 --> 26:00.955
That which we call a rose
by any other name

26:00.956 --> 26:02.523
would smell as sweet...

26:02.524 --> 26:05.293
Very, very nice.

26:05.294 --> 26:09.964
- Are you here
for the showcase?

26:09.965 --> 26:11.499
- When did you last see bing?

26:11.500 --> 26:14.769
- Um...

26:14.770 --> 26:19.674
Thursday.
Late dinner.

26:19.675 --> 26:21.175
He was like
an uncle.

26:21.176 --> 26:24.245
- An uncle?
Really?

26:24.246 --> 26:26.314
What did you two do
at his loft?

26:26.315 --> 26:28.349
- It's not-

26:28.350 --> 26:32.320
we were friends, really.

26:32.321 --> 26:35.756
- You mean...What?

26:35.757 --> 26:41.595
You provided a...
A girlfriend experience.

26:41.596 --> 26:46.200
That's what your agency
calls it, right?

26:47.302 --> 26:50.004
He was super supportive.

26:50.005 --> 26:52.940
Taught me about wines.

26:52.941 --> 26:55.910
- Do you know if he took Viagra
Thursday or Friday night?

26:55.911 --> 26:57.712
- Not with me.
He couldn't.

26:57.713 --> 26:59.347
He already
had his Nitroglycerin.

26:59.348 --> 27:00.948
- And he was careful
about that?

27:00.949 --> 27:04.285
- Oh, God, so was I.

27:04.286 --> 27:08.189
I don't feel guilty.

27:08.190 --> 27:12.560
He had an open marriage.

27:12.561 --> 27:14.662
- An open marriage?

27:14.663 --> 27:16.864
Hardly.

27:16.865 --> 27:19.066
- He had a playpen for
his call girls.

27:19.067 --> 27:23.838
- What are you guys,
the sex police?

27:23.839 --> 27:27.108
We had been married
for a long time.

27:27.109 --> 27:28.509
- Understood.

27:28.510 --> 27:31.479
