where he met prostitutes.

27:50.198 --> 27:52.767
- Not so fixed...

27:52.768 --> 27:55.469
I saw this photo
in your house.

27:55.470 --> 27:59.206
Your husband had it
blown up to poster size

27:59.207 --> 28:02.176
and then desecrated it.

28:04.646 --> 28:06.380
He had it
hung in the same room

28:06.381 --> 28:08.916
where he had
sex with call girls.

28:16.090 --> 28:18.392
When I came home
with Shane...

28:18.393 --> 28:21.228
