28:23.098 --> 28:24.398
One of his whores.
- Avery-

28:24.399 --> 28:28.335
- no. No.
- Please.

28:28.336 --> 28:30.905
I waited for her to leave.

28:30.906 --> 28:32.606
I knew that if he'd
been with a girl,

28:32.607 --> 28:36.811
