28:36.812 --> 28:40.414
I poured a glass,
I put in the nitrates,

28:40.415 --> 28:45.786
and I locked
the cellar door.

28:45.787 --> 28:48.755
I am glad he's dead.

28:52.794 --> 28:58.365
I am really, really
happy about that.

28:58.366 --> 28:59.733
- You know, Avery,

28:59.734 --> 29:02.703
we have
to take you into custody.

29:05.748 --> 29:06.748
In holding.

29:06.749 --> 29:07.816
Nice job.
You got your confession.

29:07.817 --> 29:09.150
She drugged
her husband's wine,

29:09.151 --> 29:11.219
and then locked him
in the cellar.

29:11.220 --> 29:13.421
- But she's lying.

29:13.422 --> 29:14.923
- Excuse me?

29:14.924 --> 29:17.192
- She told us that
she put his heart medicine

29:17.193 --> 29:18.693
in his wine glass.

29:18.694 --> 29:20.662
