the basement with his girl,

30:26.462 --> 30:29.430
and I sent Shane home.

30:34.870 --> 30:38.473
- You overheard your husband
with a hooker,

30:38.474 --> 30:41.409
you then you
waited for her to leave.

30:47.249 --> 30:49.818
You poisoned him.

30:49.819 --> 30:52.554
And that's your story?

30:52.555 --> 30:55.523
- Yes.

30:59.629 --> 31:00.929
- Shane Berlin?

31:00.930 --> 31:02.430
- Yeah?

31:02.431 --> 31:04.399
- Do you mind if we
come in?

31:04.400 --> 31:08.370
Thank you.

31:08.371 --> 31:10.071
You live here alone?

31:10.072 --> 31:11.706
- No,
with my girlfriend.

31:11.707 --> 31:13.408
- Your girlfriend
Avery Cullman?

31:13.409 --> 31:18.580
- What?
- Avery Cullman.

31:18.581 --> 31:22.817
- Juliet...
