31:22.818 --> 31:24.719
- What are you doing here?

31:24.720 --> 31:27.822
- We were just
talking about Avery.

31:27.823 --> 31:29.424
- You mind
if I take a look around?

31:29.425 --> 31:32.393
- No, go ahead.

31:35.631 --> 31:38.566
- So...You two
meet in acting class?

31:51.246 --> 31:53.181
- Emily, listen,

31:53.182 --> 31:56.885
this is not
off-Broadway theatre.

31:56.886 --> 31:58.987
Okay?

31:58.988 --> 32:00.622
