at felony murder.

32:00.623 --> 32:02.757
- That's crazy.
We didn't do anything.

32:02.758 --> 32:03.892
- Maybe you didn't,

32:03.893 --> 32:05.460
but we're thinking
that Shane did.

32:05.461 --> 32:08.363
That he poisoned bing,
and he left him to die.

32:08.364 --> 32:10.799
- You think
Shane was jealous?

32:10.800 --> 32:12.534
'Cause he wasn't.

32:12.535 --> 32:13.802
He knew all about
me and bing,

32:13.803 --> 32:15.170
he was cool with it.

32:15.171 --> 32:18.139
- Of course he was.

32:38.160 --> 32:41.996
- So how did it play out?

32:41.997 --> 32:46.901
You help Shane get
bing out of the picture,

32:46.902 --> 32:51.005
so that Shane
could hook up with Avery...

32:51.006 --> 32:53.475
