could bleed her dry?

32:53.476 --> 32:56.511
- I didn't want bing
out of the way.

32:56.512 --> 32:58.346
I told you, I liked him.

32:58.347 --> 33:00.582
- Like an uncle.

33:00.583 --> 33:04.319
- And bing
really, really liked me.

33:04.320 --> 33:08.823
He said I gave him
his smile back.

33:08.824 --> 33:11.793
- Really, really?

33:13.595 --> 33:16.698
- He was leaving his wife,
you know.

33:16.699 --> 33:18.166
