charges based on her confession.

33:37.086 --> 33:38.920
Shane gives her
reasonable doubt.

33:38.921 --> 33:42.423
We've got nothing.

33:42.424 --> 33:46.361
- You know, when Avery
saw the wedding photo,

33:46.362 --> 33:49.197
I mean, she looked hurt,
but she didn't look surprised.

33:54.503 --> 33:57.505
I'm gonna get a hold
of her personal belongings.

33:57.506 --> 34:00.474
We need a search warrant.

34:07.549 --> 34:11.853
Here's the man
you confessed for.

34:11.853 --> 34:14.022
He played you.

34:14.023 --> 34:16.056
- No.
Why would I kill him?

34:16.058 --> 34:17.958
- Avery says you
were in love with her.

34:17.960 --> 34:19.893
