34:19.895 --> 34:23.864
Look at me.

34:23.866 --> 34:26.868
- So maybe you were
in love with her townhouse.

34:26.869 --> 34:30.170
You were there the night
bing was killed.

34:30.172 --> 34:31.438
- She left for awhile,

34:31.440 --> 34:34.641
then came back
and asked me for a lift home.

34:34.643 --> 34:37.411
- She left the shoot?
Where'd she go?

34:37.413 --> 34:39.112
- I don't know.
- You don't know?

34:39.114 --> 34:43.251
Really?
You two were close, right?

34:43.252 --> 34:45.954
She gave you modeling jobs,
an apartment...

34:45.955 --> 34:48.889
